                &lt;p&gt;A number of years ago I bought a neat little &lt;span class=&#34;caps&#34;&gt;LCD&lt;/span&gt;/Button add-on module for my 1st Gen Raspberry Pi. The company that produced these (Emsystech Engineering, Germany) no longer produce them and they no longer host information about them on their website. This is a mirror of the info that I&amp;#8217;ve managed to collate from a number of sources, primarily the &lt;a href=&#34;https://archive.org/web/&#34;&gt;Wayback Machine&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;            </content>
